Uma usebenzisa amasevisi wethu, usithemba ngolwazi lakho. Siyaqonda ukuthi lona umthwalo omkhulu futhi sisebenza kanzima ukuvikela ulwazi lwakho futhi sikwenze ukwazi ukulilawula.Le Inqubomgomo Yobumfihlo yenzelwe ukukusiza ukuthi uqonde ukuthi uluphi ulwazi esiluqoqayo, kungani siluqoqa, nokuthi ungabuyekeza kanjani, ukhiphe, futhi ususe ulwazi lwakho.